        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "You're not doing yourself or your employer any good if you can't work effectively through burn out. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "I‚Äôm lucky enough to have a small room in the house that functions as my office, and I can shut the door and walk away. But that‚Äôs not going to protect me once my wife starts working from home later in the week. I‚Äôll be working in the living room (most likely), and will have to revert to what I did when I lived in a flat - close up the laptop, put my work notebooks and files away in a bag, and prepare the room for ‚Äúevening mode‚Äù.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "This will also stop my children destroying my work and notes through creative illustrations when they get home from school.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Get a little social interaction",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "heading",
        "tag": "h2",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "image",
        "src": "__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2020/03/61451686-4283-4B25-9A41-04DB4BF4F2B6.jpeg",
        "cardWidth": "wide"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Your ability to do this might change as the pandemic progresses, but honestly, a walk to the local coffee shop, a chat with the barista, and a walk home will make a huge difference to your working life. We‚Äôre not quite in the total lockdown where this is impossible (in the UK at least - I‚Äôm aware some readers ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "are",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ") so enjoy it while you can. My local coffee shop has actually taped up the floor to help enforce social distancing, which is helpful.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Before all this happened, going and working in the coffee shop for an hour or two was important. That might not be an option for a while, but let‚Äôs do what we can to keep those places open, shall we?",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
